## Diffusion Coefficient Estimation

The diffusion coefficient (denoted by `phi`) should be $(32/\pi)^{1/4}\approx1.786$, and the drift coefficient (denoted by `theta`) should be $\sqrt{2/\pi}\approx0.798$.

